    "summary": "In this transcript, a user describes a sudden, \"thunderclap\" style headache and asks if it is merely dehydration or a caffeine crash. The assistant repeatedly provides cautious, non-diagnostic responses, advises monitoring for red-flag neurological symptoms, and refers the user to a healthcare professional.",
